<figureCitation box="[1009,1079,1989,2011]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1950,1974]" captionTargetBox="[159,1422,1217,1924]" captionTargetId="figure-448@19.[151,1436,1209,1926]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 10. Holotype Heilus faldermanni, undetermined sex. A. dorsal view. B. lateral view. C. labels. The copyright of images belongs to NHRS." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4414706" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4414706/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
