<figureCitation box="[850,908,797,819]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="10.[151,250,972,996]" captionTargetBox="[159,1422,188,944]" captionTargetId="figure-20@10.[151,1435,181,949]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 4. Holotype Heilus inaequalis, female. A. dorsal view. B. lateral view. C. labels. The copyright of images belongs to NHRS." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4414692" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4414692/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="157">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
)................ 
